   297→/**
   298→ * POST /pm/schedule
   299→ *
   300→ * Create a new PM schedule entry.
   301→ *
   302→ * Request body:
   303→ * - trainId: UUID of train
   304→ * - pmTypeId: UUID of PM type
   305→ * - targetDate: Target date (YYYY-MM-DD)
   306→ * - assignedDepotId?: UUID of assigned depot
